text: Ciocan ("hammer") is a Romanian surname, meaning "hammer". It can refer to: *Constantin Ciocan, Romanian cyclist *Ieremia Ciocan, Romanian priest and politician *Ion Ciocan, Romanian politician *Iurie Ciocan, Moldovan politician and professor ==See also== *Ciocanu *Ciocana, a sector in Chișinău Category:Romanian-language surnames
title: Ciocan
